1ikajulaurit, ataniiq,
2sulingittunik uqausiqaqput inuuqatimingnut;
3ataniup kipititsumaaliqᐰt piujurinirngmik nilliajut,
4imaak uqaqtut, “uqattinnut saalaqarumaaqpugut;
5“ajuqsaqtut uquᒤksaqtitaungmata,
6ataniup uqausingit ilakkanniqsimanngilat,
7ataniiq, ivvit qaujisarngniaqpatit,
8piungittulijut nanituinnaq pisurajakput,
